#

Classic Beef Borscht

120 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodSoupHearty

Description

A hearty, vibrant beet soup that combines tender beef, earthy vegetables, and a touch of sour cream for creaminess.

Ingredients

  • beef chuck roast: 1 lb
  • beets: 3 medium
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrots: 2 medium
  • potatoes: 2 medium
  • onion: 1 large
  • garlic: 3 cloves
  • beef broth: 6 cups
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • fresh dill: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • bay leaf: 1
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
